data.description: This 3 bed, 3 bath, 2,339 sq. ft. house is located in between the El Centro Regional Hospital and Bucklin park    in the well established Johnston Subdivision. It not only offers TWO MASTER BEDROOMS, but TWO LIVING  ROOMS, a double-sided fireplace, a dining room, laminate flooring and a soft water system throughout the entire house. It features a swimming pool that can be heated and you also have the added benefit of energy efficiency with the many solar panels to save during those summer months. The house is close to schools and has easy access to Interstate 8. Make your appointment today for your private showing.
